    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated project or as a source for parts. It currently has significant mechanical issues that prevent it from being a reliable daily driver, and the body shows heavy wear including rust spots and significant paint deterioration. The interior requires a complete overhaul due to heavy staining and upholstery damage. This is a true fixer-upper for someone with the tools and time to invest in a full restoration.",
